 《小丑2》作曲家戏称续集中将有“很多音乐” https://www.nme.com/news/film/joker-2-composer-teases-a-lot-of-music-in-sequel-3494207?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=joker-2-composer-teases-续集中有很多音乐Adam StarkeyWed, 06 Sep 2023 15:57:50 +0000 Film NewsNewsJoker https://www.nme.com/?p=3494207 <p><img width="2000" height="1268" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Webp.net-resizeimage-29.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="小丑" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Webp.net-resizeimage-29.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Webp.net-resizeimage-29-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Webp.net-resizeimage-29-800x507.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Webp.net-resizeimage-29-696x441.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Webp.net-resizeimage-29-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Webp.net-resizeimage-29-1068x677.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该片预计明年上映</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/joker-2-composer-teases-a-lot-of-music-in-sequel-3494207">《小丑 2》的作曲家戏称续集中将有“很多音乐”，该续集</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1268" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Webp.net-resizeimage-29.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="小丑" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Webp.net-resizeimage-29.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Webp.net-resizeimage-29-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Webp.net-resizeimage-29-800x507.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Webp.net-resizeimage-29-696x441.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Webp.net-resizeimage-29-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Webp.net-resizeimage-29-1068x677.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/joker-folie-a-deux">《小丑</a>：双人舞曲》</em>的作曲家 Hildur Guðnadóttir 表示，即将上映的续集可能比预期更像一部音乐剧。</p><p>在接受<a href="https://comicbook.com/dc/news/joker-2-composer-hildur-gudnadottir-folie-a-duex-score-exclusive/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>ComicBook.com</em></a>采访时，作曲家被问及续集的音乐性质将如何影响配乐。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/joker-2-folie-a-deux-title-release-date-cast-plot-3249040">这是我们对《小丑》续集的了解</a></strong></li></ul><p>“我只能说将会有很多音乐，”古兹纳多蒂尔告诉媒体。 “这就是我能给予的全部。”</p><p>为 2019 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/joker"><em>《小丑》</em></a>配乐的古德纳多蒂尔再次回归，为续集提供配乐——此前该续集被描述为以音乐元素为特色。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Joaquin-Phoenix">杰昆·菲尼克斯 (Joaquin Phoenix)</a>在<em>《小丑：双人舞》 (Joker: Folie à Deux)</em>中回归饰演亚瑟·弗莱克 (Arthur Fleck)，与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a>饰演哈莉·奎因 (Harley Quinn)。续集由托德·菲利普斯 (Todd Phillips) 执导， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/lady-gaga-wraps-filming-on-joker-2-with-new-look-harley-quinn-3427441">于今年四月正式杀青</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CqrK_ipP18Z/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background